<div class="owner-auth-page">
    <div class="oa-card">
        <h1 class="oa-title">비밀번호 재설정</h1>
        <p class="oa-desc">
            부트스트랩 토큰을 사용해 관리자 비밀번호를 재설정합니다.
        </p>

        <form id="resetWithTokenForm" class="oa-form">
            <div class="oa-field">
                <label for="rpEmail">이메일</label>
                <input type="email" id="rpEmail" required />
            </div>

            <div class="oa-field">
                <label for="rpNewPassword">새 비밀번호 (8자 이상)</label>
                <input type="password" id="rpNewPassword" minlength="8" required />
            </div>

            <div class="oa-field">
                <label for="rpToken">부트스트랩 토큰</label>
                <input type="password" id="rpToken" required />
            </div>

            <div class="oa-actions">
                <button type="submit">비밀번호 재설정</button>
            </div>
        </form>

        <div class="oa-links">
            <a href="/owner/login">로그인으로 돌아가기</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="/static/js/owner-auth.js"></script>
